OL,3,C'Some industrial action' likely to
OL,4,Ccontinue into summer say teachers
OL,6,FTeaching unions in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fhave told UTV that some industrial
OL,8,Faction is likely to continue into the
OL,9,Fsummer term due to a delay in funds
OL,10,Fbeing approved towards a pay deal
OL,11,Fwhich they have accepted.
OL,13,FINTO, NAHT, NASUWT, NEU and UTU
OL,14,Fmembers voted in favour of a pay offer
OL,15,Fput on the table by the Education
OL,16,FMinister last week.
