OL,3,C'Some industrial action' likely to
OL,4,Ccontinue into summer say teachers
OL,6,FThe Department of Education is
OL,7,Fresponsible for taking forward that
OL,8,Finformation to the Department of
OL,9,FFinance for approval, however UTV
OL,10,Funderstands there was a delay in the
OL,11,Ftransfer of that information.
OL,13,FApproval for funding was given on
OL,14,FThursday and the final pay offer is
OL,15,Fnow expected to be ratified on Tuesday
OL,16,F9 April.
OL,18,FTeachers in Northern Ireland have not
OL,19,Fhad a pay increase for three years.
