OL,3,C'Some industrial action' likely to
OL,4,Ccontinue into summer say teachers
OL,6,FThe pay offer accepted by the five
OL,7,Fmain unions in mid-March includes an
OL,8,Fincrease to newly qualified teachers
OL,9,Fstarting salary of #30,000, with other
OL,10,Fteachers getting a cumulative 10.4%
OL,11,Fpay rise plus #1,000 consolidated pay.
OL,12,FUnions told UTV that while they
OL,13,Fwelcomed Thursday's funding approval
OL,14,Fannouncement, they had expected to
OL,15,Fratify the deal with the Department of
OL,16,FEducation on Tuesday 26 March.
