OL,3,C'Some industrial action' likely to
OL,4,Ccontinue into summer say teachers
OL,6,FMark McTaggart of INTO described it as
OL,7,Fa "good day now that the money has
OL,8,Fbeen made available to settle the
OL,9,Fdeal" but added that "it has taken
OL,10,Flonger than it should have".
OL,12,F"We expected that the deal would have
OL,13,Fbeen signed on Tuesday but that wasn't
OL,14,Favailable to us as the Finance
OL,15,FMinister hadn't had the opportunity to
OL,16,Fsign the deal off," he claimed.
OL,18,F"The industrial action will continue
OL,19,Funtil at least the 9 April when the
OL,20,Fdeal is actually signed off," the INTO
OL,21,Frepresentative added.
