OL,3,C'Some industrial action' likely to
OL,4,Ccontinue into summer say teachers
OL,6,F"We would prefer not to be on
OL,7,Findustrial action, teachers don't want
OL,8,Fto be on industrial action.
OL,10,F"You can't expect teachers to go
OL,11,Fstraight off industrial action, there
OL,12,Fare parts of industrial action which
OL,13,Fwill take slightly longer to come off.
OL,15,F"There are part of the industrial
OL,16,Faction where teachers were working to
OL,17,Frule, so they won't be changing that,
OL,18,Fso in reality, it won't be until the
OL,19,Fsummer term, after the summer
OL,20,Fholidays, for action to stop
OL,21,Fcompletely."
