OL,3,C'Some industrial action' likely to
OL,4,Ccontinue into summer say teachers
OL,6,FIn a statement issued on Thursday
OL,7,Fevening, the Education Minister Paul
OL,8,FGivan said he was "pleased that the
OL,9,FFinance Minister has approved the
OL,10,Fteachers' pay awards for 2021, 2022
OL,11,Fand 2023".
OL,13,F"This settlement, once ratified after
OL,14,Fthe Easter school break, will see the
OL,15,Fend to all industrial action by
OL,16,Fteachers and school leaders which has
OL,17,Fbeen ongoing since May 2022."
